    </p>
    <p class="result-sub-heading-2 text-purple mb-4" id="li-3a">2.1.1 Overview</p>
    <p class="font-paragraph-2 mb-4">
      Below, you’ll find a visual overview of your results: your self-assessment and feedback of others. Also there are two graphs representing the perspective from your supervisor and all others on which points to develop. They are called Developmental-supervisor and Developmental-others.
      <br> Click on the personal logbook button to get more information and/or record your insights and conclusions.
    </p>
    <div class="row mb-5 justify-content-center">
