          </td>
          <td>
            We must be transparent, share information, and show people data on everything.
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="font-weight-bold">
            Networks
          </td>
          <td>
            We need structure, rules, and control to function and get results. Only a clear top-down organizational structure will work.
          </td>
          <td>
